title: Chaos in Catalonia as Spain's police clash with independence voters
description:
Violence broke out in Catalonia as voters attempted to cast their ballots in an independence referendum. Spanish officials say the poll is illegal, and police blocked many from casting their votes. CGTN's Dan Williams reports from Barcelona.
